General.Name: Green Brick Partners Inc
General.Description: Green Brick Partners, Inc. operates as a homebuilding and land development company in the Southeast and Central United States. The company operates through three segments: Builder Operations Central, Builder Operations Southeast, and Land Development. It also acquires land for the development of residential lots. In addition, the company engages in the homebuilding process, including land acquisition and development, entitlements, design, construction, marketing, and sales and the creation of communities. Green Brick Partners, Inc. was incorporated in 2006 and is headquartered in Plano, Texas.
